NOTICE — Third-party data & attribution
Corvus Sentinel (Old Crows Wireless Solutions)
=============================================================================

This file records the provenance and license of every third-party dataset used
to train any model shipped in Corvus Sentinel, and carries the attributions
those licenses require.

It exists because Sentinel is a COMMERCIAL, life-safety product. Several of the
best-known public audio datasets are licensed NON-COMMERCIALLY, and training on
one would quietly contaminate a model we sell. Provenance is tracked here up
front so that question is answerable at any point, by anyone, without archaeology.

Maintenance rule: nothing gets trained on until it is listed below with its
license. If a dataset is not in this file, it is not cleared for use.


