2. DATASETS DELIBERATELY EXCLUDED
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------

Recorded so nobody re-litigates this, or reaches for one of these because it is
the top search result. Each was evaluated and rejected.

### UrbanSound8K — EXCLUDED (non-commercial license)
    https://urbansounddataset.weebly.com/
    License: CC BY-NC 3.0. Has a `gun_shot` class (374 clips) and is the single
    most common starting point for gunshot classifiers. The NC term forbids
    commercial use. Sentinel is sold. DO NOT USE.

### ESC-50 — EXCLUDED (non-commercial license)
    License: CC BY-NC 3.0. Has a gunshot class (40 clips). Same reason.
    DO NOT USE.

### FSD50K CC-BY-NC clips — EXCLUDED (non-commercial license)
    The NC subset of FSD50K, filtered out mechanically (see §1).

### FSD50K CC Sampling+ clips — EXCLUDED (license unclear for ML training)
    CC Sampling+ permits transformative "sampling" but restricts redistribution
    of the whole work, and its application to model training is not settled.
    Only 3.5% of the corpus — not worth the ambiguity. Excluded by default.

### Gunshot Audio Forensics Dataset (Cadre Forensics / NIJ) — NOT CLEARED
    https://cadreforensics.com/audio/  (NIJ grant 2016-DN-BX-0183)
    ~10,000 shots, 20 firearms x 20 positions x 4 devices, .22LR-.300BLK,
    caliber-labeled. Technically excellent and free with registration — but it
    carries NO LICENSE STATEMENT, only "provided as-is for use by any
    researcher." That is not a grant of commercial rights.
    STATUS: blocked pending written clarification from Cadre/NIJ. Do not train
    on it until that is in hand and recorded here.

### Multi-firearm, multi-orientation gunshot dataset — NOT CLEARED
    https://zenodo.org/record/7004819  (DOI 10.5281/zenodo.7004819)
    ~2,100 files @ 44.1 kHz, 4 firearms (AR-556 .223, Remington 870 12ga,
    .38 S&W revolver, Glock 17 9mm), captured on Raspberry Pi / ReSpeaker /
    MiniDSP UMA-8 / phones — i.e. almost exactly our planned edge-node hardware.
    STATUS: high value, license not yet verified on the Zenodo record. Confirm
    the license field before use and record it here.


